text: A gubernatorial election was held on 7 April 2019 to elect the next Governor of Mie. == Candidates == *Eikei Suzuki* back by CDP, LDP, DPFP, SDP. *Kanako Suzuki, back by the JCP. == Results == == References == Category:Gubernatorial elections in Japan Category:2019 elections in Japan Category:April 2019 events in Japan Category:Politics of Mie Prefecture
title: 2019 Mie gubernatorial election
